<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password OTP</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: 'Lucida Grande'; padding: 15px 15vw; color: #101010; background-color: #f5f5f5;">

    <h1 style="font-family: Verdana; text-align: center; font-size: 50px;">Evira</h1>
    <div style="text-align: center; ">
        <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/evira-b42be.appspot.com/o/pngs%2Fforgot-password.png?alt=media&token=bbd64dae-ac3e-44f4-8171-3e5d247a4c78"
            alt="Forgot Password PNG">
    </div>
    <h4>Hello <%= name %>,
    </h4>
    <p>Below is your OTP to reset your password</p>
    <hr>
    <h1 style="font-family: Verdana; text-align: center; font-size: 50px; margin: 25px; color: rgb(38, 66, 95);"><%= otp %>
    </h1>
    <hr>
    <p>OTP will expire in 15 minutes</p>

    <p>Thanks</p>
    <p>Team Evira</p>

    <p>
        PS: If you did not request for OTP, please ignore this email</p>

</body>

</html>